{"code":0,"message":"","data":null,"sentence":{"phonemes":[],"text":"Every mushroom has its own mastery. I could become a cat and make the girl scream for me. I could become a cockroach and make the girl scream for me. I could become a mushroom and make the girl weep for me. Admittedly, to be adored is something. But only as a mushroom can one enjoy the silent rainforest. I merely exist in stillness, watching all these passing emotions, while I remain forever unchanged.","words":[]}}
